{"type": "article", "id": 2237, "title": "多伦多设计师的厨房", "description": "", "date": "2014-09-07T23:36:03Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 2, "comment_count": 3, "praise_count": 9, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160605222300Emv5sfU91cxIGpri.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p class=\"p3\">\r\n\t<span style=\"line-height:1.5;\">Kitchen by<a href=\"http://store.mjolk.ca/index.php?ishome=1\" target=\"_blank\"> John Baker and Juli Daoust</a></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p2\">\r\n\t<span class=\"s1\">一对多伦多的设计师设计的挪威风格又带点日范儿的厨房，自然平实，充满生活气息，而且很大，让人看上去就很想在那里烹（用）饪（餐）。一些小细节是可以买到的，比如 Jonas Bohlin 设计的铜质枝形吊灯可以<a href=\"http://www.remodelista.com/products/lamp-kvist-6\" target=\"_blank\">点击这里购买</a>；Sori Yanagi 设计的烧水壶<a href=\"http://www.remodelista.com/products/sori-yanagi-kettle\" target=\"_blank\">点这里</a>；Oji Masanori 出品的锅铲篓<a href=\"http://www.remodelista.com/products/oji-masanori-brass-tool-holder-large\" target=\"_blank\">点这里</a>；Oji Masanori 锅垫<a href=\"http://www.remodelista.com/products/bagel-trivet\" target=\"_blank\">点这儿</a> ⋯⋯总之品质生活很贵。</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p2\">\r\n\t<span class=\"s1\"><img src=\"img/uploads/2016072613513557fHUFpl2TdiOQxK.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.6671875\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160726135135F2MzaVb9OPAKZuIx.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160726135136vIFhl8ZsxOQeWAG2.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.609375\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160726135136ZT3tv6pVfNQK4UyA.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.0375\" data-format=\"jpeg\"></span> \r\n</p>\n\n\n\n"}